data.description: Great trade-winds flow thru this condo featuring: • 2 Bed / 2 Bath • Laminate and Tile flooring inside • Pet friendly complex • Lanai with a narrow strip of land fenced with gate - you can grow a small herb/flower garden and also have a pet.  You can walk your pet right out of the patio to a community park right across the street half a block away. • 2 Assigned parking stalls conveniently located - One parking stall is right in front of the unit #5 with only one neighboring stall. The second parking stall #19 is right in front of the other.  • Mail box conveniently located in close proximity  - New GE stackable Washer and Dryer - New LG Stainless Steel Refrigerator  Take a look at the photos on the property website directly: https://kauai-real-estate-media.aryeo.com/sites/dalgnae/unbranded  Low monthly HOA fee of $482.02 covers water, sewer, common area landscaping and maintenance, association management, insurance, reserves, solid waste removal service and cardboard recycling.  Halelani Village is one of the few condominiums that allow pets. Located at the Heart of Lihue. Walking distance to a community park across the road, close to schools (private and public), community college, shopping center and a short drive to Beaches, Golf, Medical facilities, Costco, Grocery stores, Farmer's Market, the Airport,  Restaurants, Harbor, Gyms, the YMCA, Post Office, Banks etc. Public school bus stop is steps away from this unit.
